531
00:32:05,310 --> 00:32:09,320
Tan'er, is he the matrilocal husband?

532
00:32:09,320 --> 00:32:11,610
He really lacks of discipline.

533
00:32:11,610 --> 00:32:17,159
Well, today, I'll teach you what discipline is.

534
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:18,860
One.

535
00:32:20,030 --> 00:32:22,699
- Do you know who I am?
- Two.

536
00:32:22,699 --> 00:32:24,849
The whole Lin'an City belongs to our family!

537
00:32:24,850 --> 00:32:28,260
- Three.
- Do you believe I can have someone break your…

538
00:32:32,020 --> 00:32:34,470
Brother, are you okay?

539
00:32:39,210 --> 00:32:42,610
Go on. I'm listening.

540
00:32:42,610 --> 00:32:44,790
Break my what?

541
00:32:47,420 --> 00:32:49,439
Young Master, what happened?

542
00:32:49,439 --> 00:32:52,470
Nothing. I'm telling a rabid dog what discipline is.

543
00:32:52,470 --> 00:32:56,059
Young Master Ning, you're a gentleman.

544
00:32:56,059 --> 00:33:00,069
For the sake of the friendship between Tan'er and I, please have mercy.

545
00:33:00,790 --> 00:33:08,170
If I didn't have mercy, your brother would have died now.

546
00:33:10,490 --> 00:33:14,040
Tan'er, let's go.

547
00:33:25,300 --> 00:33:28,220
Brother, are you all right?

548
00:33:31,800 --> 00:33:33,400
Brother...

549
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:39,400
Brother!

550
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:41,900
Brother, don't be angry.
[Lou Manor]

551
00:33:42,800 --> 00:33:45,400
- Brother, are you all right?
- Don't follow me!

552
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:48,800
Today, you should have stayed in the store and taken care of the business,

553
00:33:48,800 --> 00:33:50,300
but you went out without permission,

554
00:33:50,300 --> 00:33:53,300
and even brought this rude guy home.

555
00:33:54,800 --> 00:33:57,600
You will stay at home from today.

556
00:33:57,600 --> 00:34:01,600
The Cloth Store is not your concern anymore.

557
00:34:01,600 --> 00:34:03,200
Brother...

558
00:34:06,600 --> 00:34:08,000
Brother, I know I was wrong.

559
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:09,800
You know?

560
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:12,300
Okay.

561
00:34:14,200 --> 00:34:17,600
Tomorrow, you should make an appointment with Su Tan'er alone

562
00:34:17,600 --> 00:34:19,800
to the Tori Restaurant.

563
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:21,100
Brother...

564
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:24,100
Tan'er has been married.

565
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:28,800
It's not good to do this.

566
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:30,200
Do whatever I ask!

567
00:34:30,200 --> 00:34:32,100
Cut the crap!

568
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:35,800
Steamed buns.

569
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:38,700
White and delicious steamed buns.

570
00:34:43,200 --> 00:34:46,800
People can forget all the troubles by having nice food and wine.

571
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:48,200
Young Master, why don't you eat them?

572
00:34:48,200 --> 00:34:50,000
Look. It's the Xichuan's hot and spicy tofu.

573
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:51,300
Seven stewed vegetables from Jiujiang.

574
00:34:51,300 --> 00:34:52,800
Steamed crabs from Liaodong.

575
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:54,600
We even have mushroom soup from Semu People.

576
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:56,400
It's a pity if you don't eat them.

577
00:34:56,400 --> 00:34:59,400
Lin'an... is an important town of commerce and trade connected to six cities.

578
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:01,200
It's also known as the nation's granary.

579
00:35:01,200 --> 00:35:04,200
These are just like a drop in the bucket.

580
00:35:04,200 --> 00:35:07,800
This hot and spicy beef is a real feature of Lin'an.

581
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:09,400
I really liked it when I was a child.

582
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:11,300
My dear, have a taste of it.

583
00:35:14,200 --> 00:35:15,800
It's tender.

584
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:17,800
Only Lin'an has this beef.

585
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,600
It's a pity that we can't take it back to Jiangning.

586
00:35:19,600 --> 00:35:21,800
I think maybe we can open Zhu Restaurant in Lin'an.

587
00:35:21,800 --> 00:35:23,800
