600
00:35:52,600 --> 00:35:53,800
It's not appropriate.

601
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:57,200
Let's just sell preserved eggs.

602
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:02,800
Masters and Ladies, someone asked me to bring this to you.

603
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:04,600
Please enjoy it.

604
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:07,200
Who would it be?

605
00:36:07,200 --> 00:36:08,900
No way, is it Lady Lou?

606
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:20,000
Come down!

607
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:23,200
We are coming!

608
00:36:23,200 --> 00:36:24,800
I knew it was you.

609
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:27,200
How have you been?

610
00:36:27,200 --> 00:36:28,600
Why did you come here?

611
00:36:28,600 --> 00:36:31,700
Last time Master Geng told us how good Lin'an was.

612
00:36:31,700 --> 00:36:33,200
So we came here to take a look.

613
00:36:33,200 --> 00:36:36,820
We went here for a trip. But actually, we are looking for business opportunities.

614
00:36:36,820 --> 00:36:40,400
[Lin'an Taiping Alley]

615
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:43,800
My dear, why did you bring us to Taiping Alley?

616
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:45,400
Take it easy.

617
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:48,200
You'll know in a minute.

618
00:36:56,600 --> 00:36:58,300
My dear.

619
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:04,400
My dear, mind your step.

620
00:37:13,300 --> 00:37:15,200
Have a look.

621
00:37:18,700 --> 00:37:20,200
What do you think about it?

622
00:37:20,200 --> 00:37:21,800
Do you like it here?

623
00:37:23,300 --> 00:37:25,200
